# Git and GitHub folders
**/.git
**/.github

# Docker/CI files we never want copied into image contexts (keep build contexts lean).
# NOTE: do NOT ignore the root Dockerfile/docker-compose.yml — they ARE the build
# definition for the root (panel+backend) context. Only exclude nested duplicates and
# stray compose variants that are not part of the active build.
**/docker-compose.cluster.yml
**/.dockerignore
**/.gitignore

# Documentation
**/docs
**/README.md
**/README_CN.md
**/README_JA.md
**/LICENSE

# Runtime data folders (mounted as volumes, or regenerated)
**/auths
**/logs
**/conv
**/config.yaml

# Frontend build artifacts and deps (rebuilt inside the image)
ui/node_modules
ui/dist
ui/dist-ssr
CLIProxyAPI/static/management.html

# Go build artifacts (prebuilt binaries committed for local use — not for the image)
CLIProxyAPI/CLIProxyAPI
CLIProxyAPI/CLIProxyAPI_bin

# Development / editor / agent tooling
**/bin
**/.vscode
**/.claude
**/.codex
**/.codex-worktrees
**/.gemini
**/.serena
**/.agent
**/.agents
**/.antigravitycli
**/.opencode
**/.idea
**/.junie
**/.worktrees
**/.bmad
**/_bmad
**/_bmad-output
**/skills
